name: Geekbench: Clang
description: Compiles files (8 in single-core mode, 96 in multi-core mode) of the Lua interpreter using Clang and the musl libc as the C standard library for the compiled files.The score is calibrated against a baseline score of 2,500 (Dell Precision 3460 with a Core i7-12700 processor) as per the Geekbench 6 Benchmark Internals.
